# Example .worktreeinclude — copied into each squad worktree.
#
# List the gitignored files a child subagent needs to run its
# validation_command. Everything here is copied (or symlinked, per
# worktree.symlinkDirectories) into the new worktree when /worktree adds it.
#
# Only include what the validation command actually needs — keep this tight.
# Secrets belong in a vault, not here; for dev-only placeholders use
# .env.test or similar.

.env.test
config/local.json

# Use ! to exclude subpaths that would otherwise be brought in by a broader
# pattern. Example: include everything in config/ except secrets.
# config/
# !config/secrets/
